msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"The Hardlight Energy Rifle is an energy weapon that uses a mechanism called "
"a 'photon solidification matrix'. It fires rapid-fire bolts of solidified "
"photons, and while it has a somewhat shorter range than a conventional "
"assault rifle, it is fast and extremely accurate, making it highly effective"
" in medium-range engagements."
msgstr ""

