msgid "hardlight precision rifle"
msgid_plural "hardlight precision rifles"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"An energy precision rifle that fires bolts of solidified, high-powered "
"photons. It has a shorter range and lower stopping power than other assault "
"rifles, making it harder to disrupt enemies from a distance, but its "
"improved aiming system and low noise make up for it, allowing for darting in"
" and out maneuvers."
msgstr ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight longbow"
msgid_plural "hardlight longbows"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A sleek, stringless, superalloy longbow that uses UPS power to run at high "
"efficiency. Each shot creates a string and arrow of powerful light instantly"
" through a projector. These systems provide exceptional accuracy and "
"penetration."
msgstr ""

