msgid "Gauss revolver"
msgid_plural "Gauss revolvers"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"The deserted cities of the apocalypse are dangerous, so take this revolver "
"with you. Firing a superheated metal rail, your trusty five-shot atomic "
"Gauss revolver will put holes in the heads of heavily armed bandits like no "
"other, faster than anyone else."
msgstr ""

