msgid "suppressor MK II"
msgid_plural "suppressor MK IIs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A suppressor reduces the amount of noise and muzzle flash generated by the "
"report of a firearm. Gunfire is extremely loud and can damage your hearing "
"without protection; this improved military silencer greatly suppresses the "
"sound of gunfire and improves shooting accuracy."
msgstr ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "rifling barrel"
msgid_plural "rifling barrels"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A gun barrel with an elongated spiral groove carved into the inside of the "
"barrel, which causes the bullet to rotate along the spiral groove as it "
"travels. The angular momentum from the rotation causes the bullet to follow "
"a stable trajectory that is less affected by ambient air currents and wind."
msgstr ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "barrel"
msgstr ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "shotgun choke"
msgid_plural "shotgun chokes"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A firearm attachment that tightens the muzzle diameter of a shotgun by "
"squeezing inside the muzzle buttstock. How tightly you tighten the choke "
"determines the dispersion of the shot, which is important to hunters."
msgstr ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "smart choke"
msgid_plural "smart chokes"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Smart shotgun chokes are a breakthrough in modern firearms technology, "
"utilizing an electronic control system to automatically adjust the barrel in"
" different shooting situations. Through adaptive adjustments and data "
"analysis, it maintains the optimal performance of the muzzle to improve "
"ballistics and dramatically increase hit rates."
msgstr ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "neuro trigger"
msgid_plural "neuro trigger"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Reads the user's brainwaves to ensure that the firearm fires as intended, "
"eliminating reflex time and improving hit rates."
msgstr ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "turbo charger"
msgid_plural "turbo chargers"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A high-powered accumulator that increases the output of a Gauss gun, "
"increasing its rate of fire. On the flip side, it significantly increases "
"the firearm's dispersion and recoil, making it more difficult to maneuver."
msgstr ""

